the purser's safe on C deck.

77
00:10:09,318 --> 00:10:10,402
Jimmy Hoffa's briefcase.

78
00:10:10,485 --> 00:10:12,237
A dozen other places. Guys, look,

79
00:10:12,321 --> 00:10:15,657
you're just going to have to
trust my instincts. I know we're close.

